---
---

<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <title>經典心象 | 攝影集</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --warm-bg: #fdfbf7;
      --text-color: #3e362e;
      --accent: #b8860b;
    }
    body {
      background-color: var(--warm-bg);
      color: var(--text-color);
      font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 2rem;
    }
    header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.1rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--accent);
    }
    .gallery {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .photo-item {
      background: #e5e5e5;
      aspect-ratio: 3/4;
      transition: transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
      cursor: pointer;
      overflow: hidden;
      /* 實驗性：錯位感 */
      margin-top: clamp(0px, 5vh, 100px);
    }
    .photo-item:hover {
      transform: scale(1.02) rotate(-1deg);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>心象 | Mindscape</h1>
    <p>—— 自然地景、人文街拍與哲思的凝視</p>
  </header>
  <main class="gallery">
    <div class="photo-item"></div>
    <div class="photo-item"></div>
    <div class="photo-item"></div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
